OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784035119
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 18-year-old dies
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a man died
OL,8,Ffollowing a crash between a car and an
OL,9,Foff-road bike.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police say officers were
OL,12,Fcalled to Pen Cae Crwn Road in
OL,13,FGorseinon, Swansea, on Thursday, where
OL,14,Fa man was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,16,FWhilst formal identification has not
OL,17,Fyet taken place, the family of an 18-
OL,18,Fyear-old from Swansea has been
OL,19,Finformed. A second man, aged 19, has
OL,20,Fbeen taken to hospital with injuries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
