OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784035119
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 18-year-old dies
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man from Morriston has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder,
OL,8,Fdriving a motor vehicle dangerously,
OL,9,Fdriving a motor vehicle whilst unfit
OL,10,Fthrough drugs, and driving a motor
OL,11,Fvehicle with a proportion of a
OL,12,Fspecified controlled drug above the
OL,13,Fspecified limit and remains in police
OL,14,Fcustody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
