PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784035119
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 18-year-old dies
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Danielle
OL,7,FThorne of the Major Crime
OL,8,FInvestigation Team said: "I understand
OL,9,Fthe concern in the local community as
OL,10,Fa result of this investigation and
OL,11,Fwant to thank them for their continued
OL,12,Fpatience and understanding at this
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"There is significant police activity
OL,16,Fin the area, and will continue to be
OL,17,Ffor several hours, however we are
OL,18,Fworking at pace to conduct enquiries
OL,19,Fin this complex investigation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
