PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784035119
OL,3,CMurder arrest after 18-year-old dies
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,F"Pen Cae Crwn Road is currently closed
OL,7,Fbetween Cecil Road from the junction
OL,8,Fof High Street to Pen-Cae Crwn Road to
OL,9,Fthe junction of Frampton Road.
OL,10,FBrighton Road, Brynteg Road and
OL,11,FPontardulais Road are also closed.
OL,13,F"We have significant resources working
OL,14,Fto lift these road closures as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible. I ask residents in need
OL,16,Furgent egress or entry to please speak
OL,17,Fto an officer at the scene who will
OL,18,Fsupport you as required."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
